To find the important features and gain insights into the interaction of them in enhancing the eWOM for MGC activities on Twitter, respectively, we applied the Logistic regression analysis [16] and the Association rule [17,18,19] to analyze the tweets gathering from four banks official Twitter account. The first methodology is powerful in identifying all key features which highly correlate with the eWOM activities. In additional, the second one can pinpoint the relationship amongst them which can cause more effective eWOM.
